[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-03T21:54:54+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/09/Star-Wars-Outlaws-Screen-Shot-8-20-24-1.54-PM.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Ubisoft rolled out a massive update for <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/star-wars/443727/star-wars-outlaws-proves-you-can-still-be-star-wars-without-the-jedi\">Star Wars Outlaws</a></em> on Thursday, addressing a long list of complaints about the open-world Star Wars game as the first step in its <a href=\"https://x.com/StarWarsOutlaws/status/1839696602056814661\">previously announced roadmap</a> to improve the game. If you haven\u2019t finished <em>Star Wars Outlaws</em> yet \u2014 maybe because you were annoyed by the game\u2019s wonky <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/star-wars-outlaws-guides\">stealth and speeder mechanics</a> \u2014 this patch might j", "id": 1263258, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/gaming/460554/star-wars-outlaws-stealth-speeder-bugs-patch", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Big Star Wars Outlaws patch fixes a long list of launch issues", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-03T21:10:34+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Electronic Arts\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/Untitled-design-2024-10-03T165209.630.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>The Sims 4</em>\u2019s next expansion is set to arrive on Halloween and, as is appropriate for such a spooky season, the expansion is all about the specter of death. <a href=\"https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/life-and-death-expansion-pack\">On Thursday, Electronic Arts released some more information</a> on what players can expect from <em>Life and Death</em>, a new expansion that includes the town of Ravenwood, new mortality-related gameplay goals, and a chance to become the Grim Reaper.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Sims have always been able to die \u2014 usually in ridiculous ways, like being chewed on by", "id": 1263259, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/460517/sims-4-life-death-grim-reaper-playable", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The Sims 4\u2019s next expansion lets you be the Grim Reaper and save souls", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-03T19:38:39+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"An image showing the spines of the hardcover leatherbound books included with this Lord of the Rings set.\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/LOTR-Illustrated-1.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>The Lord 